---
// Print-only replacement for PlantIndigoViewer.
// Replaces the interactive 3D WebGL viewer with a static render PNG.
// The feature grid and flat-structure diagram below are already static — kept as-is.
---
<div style="margin-bottom:0.75rem">
  <img src="/images/mol-plant-ind-large.png" alt="Indigotin — 3D molecular structure" style="width:100%;display:block;border-radius:4px;background:#0d1b2a" />
</div>

<hr class="mol-divider" />
<div class="flat-label">Key structural features</div>
<div class="feature-grid">
  <div style="background:#0a100a;border:1.5px solid #e8c000;border-radius:6px;padding:.7rem;text-align:center">
    <div style="font-family:var(--ff-mono);font-size:.6rem;color:#e8c000;margin-bottom:.3rem">CHROMOPHORE</div>
    <div style="font-size:1.6rem;font-family:'Courier New',monospace;color:#e8c000;font-weight:700">C=C</div>
    <div style="font-size:.7rem;color:#8a8060;margin-top:.3rem">center of molecule<br/>source of blue color</div>
  </div>
  <div style="background:#080a20;border:1.5px solid #4488ff;border-radius:6px;padding:.7rem;text-align:center">
    <div style="font-family:var(--ff-mono);font-size:.6rem;color:#6a8aff;margin-bottom:.3rem">H-BOND DONOR</div>
    <div style="font-size:1.6rem;font-family:'Courier New',monospace;color:#4488ff;font-weight:700">N–H</div>
    <div style="font-size:.7rem;color:#6a7090;margin-top:.3rem">×2, one per half<br/>causes insolubility</div>
  </div>
  <div style="background:#200808;border:1.5px solid #ff6666;border-radius:6px;padding:.7rem;text-align:center">
    <div style="font-family:var(--ff-mono);font-size:.6rem;color:#ff7060;margin-bottom:.3rem">H-BOND ACCEPTOR</div>
    <div style="font-size:1.6rem;font-family:'Courier New',monospace;color:#ff6666;font-weight:700">C=O</div>
    <div style="font-size:.7rem;color:#907070;margin-top:.3rem">×2, one per half<br/>causes insolubility</div>
  </div>
</div>

<hr class="mol-divider" style="margin:.8rem 0" />
<div class="flat-label">Full flat structure — key features annotated</div>
<img src="/diagrams/m3/indigotin-flat-annotated.svg" alt="Indigotin flat structure, annotated" style="width:100%;display:block;border-radius:6px" />
<div class="dp-cap">
  The flat diagram shows the complete indigotin structure with all key groups highlighted:
  the C=C chromophore (gold, center), the N-H hydrogen bond donors (blue, circled),
  and the C=O carbonyl acceptors (red, circled).
</div>

<style>
  .feature-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: .7rem;
    margin: .5rem 0;
  }
</style>
